<item>
            <title>[LU-19589] FLR-EC: add &apos;lfs find&apos; support for EC files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19589</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We will need to add support for &lt;b&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lfs find&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to find files based on their parity settings and the &lt;tt&gt;LOV_PATTERN_PARITY&lt;/tt&gt; pattern type. This likely means adding an option such as &lt;b&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;ec&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, allowing searches for layouts like &lt;b&gt;8+2 (and 8:2)&lt;/b&gt; or similar (e.g., &lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;ec 8+2&lt;/tt&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
